The fix is small and catalog-preserving: `@std/jsonc` is a package-local JSR import, matching the existing `@std/*` declarations in member `deno.json` files. I’m adding it back to `packages/config/deno.json`, then I’ll rerun the focused config test and the full root task.
apply patch
